<h2>Lard Pastry</h2>

<div>
	<h3>Ingredients</h3>

	<ul>
		<li>400g plain flour</li>
		<li>100g unsalted butter</li>
		<li>100g lard</li>
		<li>60g granulated sugar (optional)</li>
		<li>shake of table salt (optional)</li>
	</ul>
</div>

<div>
	<h3>Method</h3>

	<ul>
		<li>Sift flour, sugar and salt into a bowl</li>
		<li>Mix in butter and lard until crumbly</li>
		<li>Slowly add in cold water, mix until doughy</li>
		<li>Roll out and use</li>
	</ul>
</div>

Link to this recipe: http://jsrn.net/tablecloth/#baking/lard_pastry